== Asismel ==
Tamaziɣt Tarifant temrawas (tettemcabi) es waṭas ar Tmaziɣt [[Tacawit]] yellan deg ugafa ogmiḍ en [[Dzayer]] acku i snat nsent llant seg Tmaziɣt Taznat (''Zenata''). Akken daɣen yella waṭas en ummerwas gar-as ed [[Taqbaylit|Teqbaylit]] ed Tmaziɣt en Tunest ed Libu Agafay ed Tmaziɣt en Siwa. 

== Tukza tasirant (tonṣibt) es Tmaziɣt en Arif==

Tamaziɣt Tarifant deg Murakuc (Merruk) d-tutlayt tasirant (tonṣibt) seg 2011 akked Tmaziɣt en Aṭlas ed Sus deg yiwet en "Tutlayt Tamaziɣt" yeddukklen. 

Daɣen llant kra en [[Tiddukla|tiddukliwin]] tidelsanin deg yiɣeṛman en [[Mlilt]] ed [[Sebta]] (yellan saddu usehres Aseppanyul) ssuturent seg udabu Aseppanyul en yiɣeṛman nni asessira (asenṣeb) en Tamaziɣt Tarifant acku azal en 40% en yimezdaɣ en [[Mlilt]] ed 25% en yimezdaɣ wn [[Sebta]] ttmeslayen es Tmaziɣt Tarifant, akken daɣen yeqqaṛ useqqamu en Tiddukla en Oṛoppa tukza en Tmaziɣt Tarifant d-akken-it d-tutlayt en tdersi acku sin iɣeṛman nni teṭṭef iten Seppanya yellan d-agmam deg Tiddukla en Oṛoppa. 

== Anagraw en tira ==

Tamaziɣt Tarifant tettwaru es yisekkilen ilatinen deg Mlilt ed Arif. 

== Abdar en wawalen ==
Imgirrden ger Tmaziɣt Tarifant ed tutlayin timaziɣin nniḍen:

* /l/ yettuɣal /ř/, amedya : '''awal''' -> '''awař'''

* Wer neqqar ara /r/ asmi yella sdat i teɣṛit: ''tadda'''r'''t'' -> ''tadd'''aa'''t''. 

Lemmer tella teɣṛit deffer /r/ ad et nɣeṛ, amedya : neqqaṛ /r/ di ''abrid''.

* /ll/ yettuɣal /dj/, amedya : '''yelli-s''' -> '''yedji-s'''.

* /lt/ yettuɣal /č/, amedya : '''weltma-s''' -> '''wečma-s'''.

* Es umata /k/ yettuɣal /c/. 

* Es umata /g/ yettuɣal /j/. 

* Aṭas en tikwal, wer neqqaṛ ara awṣil ''a-'', amedya : '''afus''' -> '''fus'''. 

